Looping Stement:
  For Loop
  While Loop
  
Looping Statement - It is used to perform same task for the required no.of.times and increase value for each tym of loop.

Mandatory - for, while loop:
      Initialisation
      Condition
      Increment/Decrement
      
Syx:
  initialisation
  while condition:
    body
    increment/decrement

For loop:
  Use Range function along with for loop.
  
syx:
  for variable in condition:
    body


Note: If the required tym of a loop is known then go for "while" loop. If not "for" loop.
